*scim-0.9.0 (07 Feb 2004)

  07 Feb 2004; Alastair Tse <liquidx@gentoo.org> scim-0.9.0.ebuild:
  version bump. fixed gconf useflag settings, added blurb about enable both GTK2
  and XIM at the same time.

